{"tid":1644100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非進化］ 關於全港感謝祭嘅建議","createTime":"2019-10-10T12:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:11:16.000Z","uid":164055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3931cb779785ce387f096d04c333cbcd2b8269be","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"首先感謝祭依種另類嘅遍地開花 的確 好有效抵抗政府想打造宵禁嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係唔知有冇手足同我一樣覺得黃店太多 個肚容量太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後我又諗點樣將感謝日<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跳出舒適圈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（理論上只有黃會響應感謝日）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後比我同時解決依兩個問題嘅方法</span></span> &mdash; 係黃店買完野食之後 聚埋一齊派比附近市民（唔理佢藍定黃）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聚埋係方便傳媒報導， 當然仍然係遍地開花 唔聚死一區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先可以支持黃店 同唔會令個肚太飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要係想打破政府想營造宵禁嘅效果 同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 對外宣傳 我地唔係只係識裝修 同時想社會和諧 所有野係政府搞出黎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位討論下可唔可行 每個月搞一次都幾和味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f20b9bd657fde81b4f6b4cfa088302b690b362eb","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"1b280f3602b5aefe6cdfc4a52ffb761bdcbab344","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"推 （2/10）"},{"pid":"7da999b83fbc3755dd6d486b1cb39853897f371b","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"推 （3/10）"},{"pid":"e675cab8355d083167a6eddcc485b9daf4e370ee","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"推 （4/10）"},{"pid":"9ef1feb9398ecb9b73aefeb644fe7badde24a5f7","tid":1644100,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"OK喎"},{"pid":"4a66f57b784625cda9149ec6524985a967ee8e25","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"勇武bb 更努力 和理非要努力cover佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a2feadca84036250b5ce102acef677ec881b9d","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勇武bb <span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>努力 和理非要努力cover佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bb54210bc0e66f7b4861b742cbadcc17879f2a4c","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"db15206c77eb23624b048e6e42cf55f79c12a6a4","tid":1644100,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"5f619713f74f7caa741c0db0af2bcce670e57dcb","tid":1644100,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"推 6/10"},{"pid":"6776d1f5e2627507e67f9ab94888757068163350","tid":1644100,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9577256507a7197ffc4c10905d0cb99476873a3c","tid":